Package: testIsLoadedDownstream
Title: Helper for the isNamespaceLoaded() Regression Test (Downstream)
Version: 1.0
Author: R Core
Maintainer: R Core <R-core@almost.r-project.org>
Description: Used by reg-packages.R to exercise isNamespaceLoaded() during
 cyclic namespace loading.  Its .onLoad can trigger a load of
 testIsLoadedUpstream while this package is itself still loading.
Imports: testIsLoadedUpstream
License: GPL (>= 2)
NeedsCompilation: no
